main.description: An online-ticketed event platform powered by blockchain. After winning the Theta Hackathon, HarkTV will be moving on to ticketed events (powered by NFTs) while using the Theta technology to raise money for charity.

main.title: MoonJelly
main.description: An extendible chrome extension that interacts with Ocean Protocol's data economy. It makes it easy to mint datatokens, get datatoken alerts, view & search the market, and see your datatoken wallet.
